The sensor_sim 's' has the signal outputs 'sensor1', 'sensor2', 'sensor3', 'sensor4', and 'timebase'. It also has a clock 'clk'.

The detector 'det' has the signal inputs 'sensor1', 'sensor2', 'sensor3', 'sensor4', and 'timebase'. It has the signal output 'hole_detected'. It also has a clock 'clk'.

The display 'd' has the signal input 'hole_detected'. It also has a clock 'clk'.

All the signals are traced in a 'wave.vcd' file.

The simulation duration for each file are:

10kmph.txt : 28590;

20kmph.txt : 17360;

30kmph.txt : 14700;

40kmph.txt : 14650;

10kmphb.txt : 15920;
